<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
    <title>Register</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="scroll-text">
      <p>General Assembly WC-SEIR-726</p>
      <p>Froy Rodriguez + Michael Hamilton
      <p>DONDA presents:</p>
      <p id="underline">A Node EJS Express MongoDB Project</p>

      <p>Express Application that renders HTML pages from EJS Templates. CRUD routes using the REST convention.
        Templating EJS to render objects from MongoDB in the browser as HTML templates.
        MongoDB persist two models. One model includes full CRUD functionality.
        Bootstrap, Heroku and Authentication.
        Users are able to the choose either side of the force. Sign in and post about their day in a galaxy far, far
        away....
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h1 class="text-center">JEDI | SITH</h1>
  <hr>

<section id="force">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
        <div class="card jedi">
          <img src="photos/tano.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="avatar">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Jedi Knight</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Ahsoka Tano, Togruta female former Jedi Padawan who, after the Clone Wars, helped establish a
              network of
              various rebel cells against the Galactic Empire</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
          <div class="card sith">
            <img src="photos/maul.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="avatar">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Sith Lord</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Darth Maul, Dathomirian Zabrak male who established himself as a crime lord during the reign of the Galactic Empire</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="form">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-8 col-md-6 col-lg-4 m-5">
        <fieldset>Sign Up</fieldset>
        <hr>
        <form action="/users/registration" method="POST">
          <fieldset class="form-row">
            <div>
              <label for="force">Choose:</label>
              <select name="force" id="force" class="form-select">
                <option selected>Force</option>
                <option value="Jedi Knight">Ahsoka Tano</option>
                <option value="Sith Lord">Darth Maul</option>
              </select><br />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="username">Username</label>
              <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="username" required /><br />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="email">Email</label>
              <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="email" /><br />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="password">Password</label>
              <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="password" id="password" /><br />
            </div>
            <div id="desc">
              <label for="bio"></label>
              <textarea name="bio" cols="30" rows="10" placeholder="Add Bio" required></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Login</button>
          </fieldset>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<hr>
<footer class="text-center">
  <ul>
    <li>Already a member?</li>
    <li><a href="/">Sign In</a></li>
  </ul>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
